               <msItemStruct xml:id="ACD1" defective="false">
                  <locus n="1">4r-8r</locus>
                  <title xml:lang="bg">Видение на цар Амфилохий</title>
                  <filiation type="protograph">Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <filiation type="antigraph">Middle Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <sampleText xml:lang="cu">
                     <head>Видѣнїе Амфилѡга царѧ Аравїе</head>
                     <incipit defective="false">Гл҃еть Баронїи хронографъ римскїи</incipit>
                  </sampleText>
               </msItemStruct>
               <msItemStruct xml:id="ACD2" defective="false">
                  <locus n="2">8v-15r</locus>
                  <title xml:lang="bg">Тълкувание за проскомидията на Симеон Солунски</title>
                  <author>Symeon of Thessalonike</author>
                  <filiation type="protograph">Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <filiation type="antigraph">Middle Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <sampleText xml:lang="cu">
                     <head>Ѿ книги с҃таго Сѵмеѡна Ѳесалонитскаго: ѡ ꙗже какѡ подобает
                с҃щенику творити с҃тꙋю проскомидїю , что знаменꙋет роскомидїѧ и
                гдѣ подобает строити роскомидїю</head>
                     <incipit defective="false">Гл҃еть с҃тыи Сѵмеѡнъ ѳесалонитскїи митрополит ѡдѣѧвшꙋсѧ
                с҃щенникꙋ..</incipit>
                  </sampleText>
               </msItemStruct>
               <msItemStruct xml:id="ACD3" defective="false">
                  <locus n="3">17r-21v</locus>
                  <title xml:lang="bg">Гръмник Зодиак</title>
                  <note place="foot" xml:id="note1"> The text presents the type of Thunderbook, predicting by the
              zodiac circle. It contains a table of the days ruled by the
              different sighs of the zodiac accordig to the twelve months. The
              table is typical of this kind of Thunderbook. The earliest
              Thunderbook which belongs to this type is in <name type="ms" full="yes">Dragolov sbornik</name>. There is a short text with
              correspondence between zodiac and different geographical places.
              It stands after the table. </note>
                  <filiation type="protograph">Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <filiation type="antigraph">Middle Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <sampleText xml:lang="cu">
                     <head>Начало громовника</head>
                     <incipit defective="false">м҃ць мартъ имѣеть а҃ в҃ рыбꙋ.</incipit>
                     <explicit defective="false">
                        <supplied>водолеи</supplied>
                        <gap/> и мꙋжемъ избраннымъ преложеніе.</explicit>
                  </sampleText>
               </msItemStruct>
               <msItemStruct xml:id="ACD4" defective="false">
                  <locus n="4">21v-30v</locus>
                  <title xml:lang="bg">Гадание по месеци</title>
                  <note place="foot" type="articleData" xml:id="note2">The text is wrongly titled
              as Lunary. In fact, it contains predictions by the phases of the
              moon, thunder, lightning, mist, earthquake for each month. The Old
              Slavic names of the months are represented here together with the
              Latin ones (i.e. <phr xml:lang="cu">Октѡмврьі рекомьй
                листопадъ</phr>). The predictions by the thunder coincide with
              the text of the Thunderbook by means of the months from
                <soCalled>Loveški Sbornik</soCalled> of <name type="personal" full="yes">Paxomios</name>
                  </note>
                  <filiation type="protograph">Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <filiation type="antigraph">Middle Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <sampleText xml:lang="cu">
                     <head>Здѣ да ꙋвѣси кїи мс҃ць есть бꙋренъ или кой сꙋшенъ или
                зименъ, и что приносѧть добро или зло и каѧ лꙋна права или
                полога</head>
                     <incipit defective="false">М҃цъ <sic>септемрїй</sic> рекомый рꙋѧнъ. Раждаетсѧ въ а҃
                часъ дне, луна егѡ свѣтить</incipit>
                     <explicit defective="false">мнози востанꙋть и брань бꙋдеть</explicit>
                  </sampleText>
               </msItemStruct>
               <msItemStruct xml:id="ACD5" defective="false">
                  <locus n="5">30v-31v</locus>
                  <title xml:lang="bg">Коледник</title>
                  <note place="foot" type="articleData" xml:id="note3">Type of Kalendologion
              without political predictions.</note>
                  <filiation type="protograph">Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <filiation type="antigraph">Middle Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <sampleText>
                     <head>Сеи Календарь</head>
                     <incipit defective="false">Аще бꙋдетъ Р҃ж<seg rend="sup">д</seg>ство Хр҃тово въ
                неделю </incipit>
                     <explicit defective="false">и запаленіе многѡ и лѣто градомъ віемо велми, жита на
                мѣста. Конець календарѧ</explicit>
                  </sampleText>
               </msItemStruct>
            </msContents>
